Class StaticImports

java.lang.Object
com.google.errorprone.bugpatterns.StaticImports
public final class StaticImports extends Object
Logic for inspecting static imports used by NonCanonicalStaticImport, NonCanonicalStaticMemberImport, and UnnecessaryStaticImport.

  • Method Details

    • tryCreate

      public static @Nullable StaticImports.StaticImportInfo tryCreate(ImportTree tree, VisitorState state)
      Returns a StaticImports.StaticImportInfo if the given import is a static single-type import. Returns null otherwise, e.g. because the import is non-static, or an on-demand import, or statically imports a field or method.
